(28007, ' Dear Pak Gunners,\nThe all inclusive package for wild boar hunting is quite expensive because it includes all the expenses incurred for paying the wages of beaters plus their food, transport, complete body wear including clothing, boots, protective jackets, caps & spears, ..etc (we use 20 to 30 beaters for a group so this becomes a big amount) plus we have to pay for the accommodation, food and transport for the hunters plus pay for their their hunting licenses, guides''s fees, cost of complete camping gear, like tents, kitchen gear, crockery, cutlery and we also have to pay for the wages for cooks ...etc. All this sums up to a big amount and obviously since this is my profession, I''ve to add sufficient profit to pay my bills, govt fees and taxes. etc. Such packages are usually affordable for our foreign clients, However, as a gesture of goodwill to my Pak Gunners I''ll work our a subsidized package ... Yet ... please note it won''t be too cheap & I must cover my costs and overheads. So I''ll give you the prices in next couple of days. \n\n[img]http://i560.photobucket.com/albums/ss46/pakistanguides/DSC02080-L.jpg[/img]\n\nYou see my beaters are properly clothed & equipped with first aid & emergency backup & this costs money !\n\n[img]http://i560.photobucket.com/albums/ss46/pakistanguides/DSC02157-L.jpg[/img]\n\n[img]http://pakistanguides.com/boar/boar_photos/global_hunting_resources_s2.JPG[/img]\n\n[img]http://pakistanguides.com/boar/photo_gallery/images/westfalia_jagdreisen_boar_hunt_37L.JPG[/img]', ''),
