(28128, ' @12gauge, \n\nI never questioned comparing RUSSIAN gun with a TURKISH, as i am of the opinion that a BAIKAL is better than any TURKISH gun. But there were few other things that i don''t agree with.\n\n1- Darra made guns are no where close to Turkish guns.\n\n2- Russians never won skeet olympics four times in a row not even four times ever since the introduction of skeet in olympics in1968 they have won only one skeet gold and that was in 1968 olympics courtesy to PETROVE he finished 2nd in 1972 olympics. Althoug Russians have bagged two more golds in Trap shooting in fourty years even they canot make it four.\n\n3-Baikal never made those competition guns that Russians used rather KBP made those guns TsKIB SOO is a subsidery of KBP those guns are not imported in Pakistan they are not IZM but MTs.\n\n4- KBP does not make cheap guns like Baikal but is considered as Holland&Holland or Perdi of Russia.\n\n5-In Beijing one Russian won a bronze but he was shooting with PERAZZI(ALIPOVE ALEXY). :|', ''),
