(28253, ' thank you guys, you all are so kind.\n\n@kagefox: double edged, peshawar, PKR 1300 (back in 2006)\n\n@12 guage: :D :D :D me too bro, l m in love with this one. will shot close ups when i get home today. what sort of close ups do you want? i ve never photographed weapons before so if you want something specific, let me know.\n\n@irttyza: dont get me wrong, the winchester 1200 is a very good weapon. The reason i dont like it is my rem 870 magnum :D\nitss sooo much more solid, sooo much more balanced, soo much more crisp than the winchester that I have started to ignore my winchester. I have fired damaged / miss fired cartridges from my 870 without any failure, have never had a single failure, ever!. the over all feel of the 870 is like a very well made weapon with superior craftsmanship. the winchester feels like a factory made weapon aimed for mass production (plastic and all) when compared to the wingmaster. with the 870, the pieces just fit so beautifully together and then every thing clicks. the sounds that it makes ....\ni think i should stop now. :) and i think i m totally in love with this one :)\n\nso in short, the overall feel of the 870 is superior than the winchester.  and thats the only reason why i dont like winchester, otherwise winchester is also a very well made and reliable SG.', ''),
