(28646, ' OK to all members, granted you people do not know me but please heed my  advise.  I was involved in the intial start of this company along with  many many other from Darra.  We used to have meetings in Lahore,  Islamabad, and Peshawar.  It was a project started by P. Musharraf like  the IDEAS project.  However, in this case thing took a turn for the  worse.  There was talk of having a proper center in or around Darra with  machines, investment casting and many many other top line stuff.  It  never panned out.  There was a R. Col. ZilurRehman and R. Brig. Naveed  Rehman who headed this shindig.  Due to various reasons and finger  pointing... the entire project has been handed over to a foundary owner  in Peshawar.  Now what is happening is: If you can''t get a visa to a  foriegn country - go and register with these guys and get your visa to -  germany, turkey, greece, dubai, france, UK, and USA... where ever there  is an international exhibition of arms.  This is ALL thats happened  since the handover over a year ago.  I can only guess ALL the money is  eaten up.  If not then the interest from that money is keeping the image  alive.  The top two control the money.  UPtill now there has been NO  Technical center, no machines, NOTHING.', ''),
