(28731, ' Salams,\n\nAt last night''s GTG Imu10 offered to take me on a hunt a couple of hours later. How could I refuse such a tempting offer from our very own PakGuns Hunting expert. We left Karachi at 6am and went on a short Wild boar hunt to Saeedpur which is located in Tando Muhammad Khan District.\n\nIt was great 90 minute hunt as I was in hurry to get back to work. Thanks Imu10 the hunt was absolutely fantastic ! Please post pictures for all of us.\n\nHere''s a Map of where it is:\n\n[img]http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/thumb/e/e5/TMKhan.jpg/800px-TMKhan.jpg[/img]', ''),
