(28806, ' [quote=Hamid]Guys, I have a Punjab licence but didnt register it in the post office. I want to renew it now. Will there be any complications?[/quote]\nAt first get the time extention from the ARMs branch in Lahore. Maximum time allotted to register in post office is one month.\nAfter getting the time extention get a copy of your license verified by the Arms branch in Lahore.\nAnd than goto your nearest post office, along with original license, CNIC photocopy, and a verified copy of your provincial license. Get te renewal tickets and your license stamped with endorsement details and than you are done.', ''),
