(28825, ' It was very unfortunate that I wasnt able to attend the special GTG due to some personal commitment, though I really wanted to be a part again.\nSecondly i wasnt able to register my non-availablility as due to some cookie error I have not been able to login from my home since quite sometime (though i have tried to check every setting that allow cookies...can someone help).\n\nAnyhow there is always a next time, hopefully will see you guyz soooooon.', ''),
(28826, ' Kaiser Khan Sahib, your threads are a ''MUST'' see every time I visit Pakguns. And this ''MUST'' means both, the one in English & the Urdu. ;)\n\nAs some members have already mentioned, its hard to put good feelings into words that we have while watching & reading your pictures & comments. But at least let me try to justify it with some yet unjustified words for that. I would say, the shared aspects of your professional exposure & lifestyle are remarkable & splendid. Some are awesome, overwhelming & breathtaking. And the rest are just amazing.\n \nMost of all, your credit is the introduction of professional standards & norms of hunting to our elite online gun enthusiasts community.\n\nI saw your hunts'' pictures quite some time back, long before Pakguns started. And at that time I wished that such standards of hunting should be somehow introduced to the masses. For clarification to the readers & not you, I''m not referring to the expensive part of it but the ''selective & limited'' hunting rather than ''bag what you can'' & ''shoot what you see'' culture.\n\nLast but of course not the least, I would like to appreciate the time you spare to explain & share your experience with the rest of us.', ''),
