(28852, ' There is a Hunting Season that specifies the dates and months that Huntibng is open. This is primarily for Birds that are migratory or permanent. Usually in Punjab Hunting is allowed only during October 15 and Februaury 15th. For the rest of the months its closed. So wait till Oct 15th and the season will start again.\n\nIn Sindh the period is Nov to Jan for most birds but Quails ae allowed aug onwards and ducks till february.', ''),
