(28883, ' My Dear Pak Gunners !\nI conducted a wild boar driven hunt in January this year for two of my German clients Fischer & Helmut.\nThey shot 64 boars in a 4 day hunt which was extended for another day because they liked it so much. \nWe could only retreive 54 boars whereas, 10 of them fell into rivers & ditches not accessible. \nThis score does not include approx 17 to 18 injured boars who managed to escape. \nI''m showing you just the selected photos of some of the bigger boars ... showing all of them will be too much ! \nOut of this harvest, we got 8 large sized trophies between 18 & 22 cms, and 12 medium sized trophies between 12 & 16 cms and the remaining 11 trophies were less than 10 cms long. \nWe used 18 beaters and 12 dogs for this hunt. Only 6 boars were shot at night using spot/flash lights. \nMy client Helmut used Blazer 338 but was not so happy because his magazine could only give him 4+1 shots and he missed lots of boars while loading his gun, whereas, his fellow hunter Fischer used the Semi Automatic Wichester 30.06 with large magazine carrying 11 shots .(plus a spare loaded magazine) .. so obviously he had an edge over Hlelmut and had a better score.\n\n[img]http://pakistanguides.com/boar/photo_gallery/images/westfalia_jagdreisen_boar_hunt_26L.JPG[/img]\n\nThis is Fischer proudly exhibiting his 22 + 22.5 cm long wild boar trophy he harvested ij Jan 2009\n\n[img]http://pakistanguides.com/boar/photo_gallery/images/westfalia_jagdreisen_boar_hunt_8L.JPG[/img]\n\n[img]http://pakistanguides.com/boar/photo_gallery/images/westfalia_jagdreisen_boar_hunt_34L.JPG[/img]\n\n[img]http://pakistanguides.com/boar/photo_gallery/images/westfalia_jagdreisen_boar_hunt_33L.JPG[/img]\n\n[img]http://pakistanguides.com/boar/photo_gallery/images/westfalia_jagdreisen_boar_hunt_24L.JPG[/img]\n\n[img]http://pakistanguides.com/boar/photo_gallery/images/westfalia_jagdreisen_boar_hunt_35L.JPG[/img]\n\nMy sons thoroughly enjoyed this wild boar hunt and it was a great experience for them.\n\n[img]http://pakistanguides.com/boar/photo_gallery/images/westfalia_jagdreisen_boar_hunt_21L.JPG[/img]\n\n[img]http://pakistanguides.com/boar/photo_gallery/images/westfalia_jagdreisen_boar_hunt_30L.JPG[/img]\n\n[img]http://pakistanguides.com/boar/photo_gallery/images/westfalia_jagdreisen_boar_hunt_19L.JPG[/img]\n\n[img]http://pakistanguides.com/boar/photo_gallery/images/westfalia_jagdreisen_boar_hunt_23L.JPG[/img]\n\n[img]http://pakistanguides.com/boar/photo_gallery/images/westfalia_jagdreisen_boar_hunt_22L.JPG[/img]\n\n[img]http://pakistanguides.com/boar/photo_gallery/images/safari_international_boar_hunt_4L.jpg[/img]\n\n[img]http://pakistanguides.com/boar/photo_gallery/images/westfalia_jagdreisen_boar_hunt_10L.JPG[/img]\n\n[img]http://pakistanguides.com/boar/photo_gallery/images/safari_international_boar_hunt_3L.jpg[/img]\n\n[img]http://pakistanguides.com/boar/photo_gallery/images/westfalia_jagdreisen_boar_hunt_29L.JPG[/img]\n\n[img]http://pakistanguides.com/boar/photo_gallery/images/westfalia_jagdreisen_boar_hunt_25L.JPG[/img]\n\n[img]http://pakistanguides.com/boar/photo_gallery/images/westfalia_jagdreisen_boar_hunt_37L.JPG[/img]\n\n[img]http://pakistanguides.com/boar/photo_gallery/images/westfalia_jagdreisen_boar_hunt_32L.JPG[/img]\n\nI think these are enough for today but I''ll revert soon and show you guys some more photos of my wild boar hunt that I conducted for my American and Italian hunters .... I hope you''ll like these pix ...... have Fun !', ''),
