(28972, ' Guys, \n\nStop behaving like Chicken Little and worrying that the sky is falling. It is not. Ban or no ban. Its the off season. So no shikar anyways. \n\n@Bluff, \n\nThat ban in India is useless. There is more poaching now than ever before. People now dont use guns, but rather use snares and traps - silent and deadly. If the objective was to save animals. The official strategy is a failure. As for prosecuting Salman Khan  for shooting blackbuck and Nawab Pataudi for shooting hare.  That was more political than anything, especially in Nawab Pataudi''s case. For these two men who were publicised, there are literally thousands of others who get away. Not because the are rich, but because they are have poor and have little media value.', ''),
