(28988, ' Its getting hot here! :) Lemme take you all in to the background of the imposed BAN so you would all understand it! After season opener most of "US" acted like meat collectors. Tilla Gang tehsil opened after 5 years as I know and all of the hunting parties knowing the potential ran towards that particular area and if someone can second me....they really destroyed the area! On my very first trip I counted like 30 JEEPS! roaming there and destroying harvested lands and shooting partridges like anything! Big limits were kept in Licences and not followed at all! Scores of couple of hunting parties were like 200, 150, 100 "THATS SINGLE PARTY''S SCORE!"\nAs mentioned earlier WLD in panic could not think of better option but to impose COMPLETE BAN! They were helpless as they could not do anything else to put hunting at hault before the announced dates! Locals at such thesils (where other than hunting..hunters detroyed their harvested lands) protested and blocked the roads and raised voices. Complaints were forwarded to WLD departments by WLD game watchers. People with considerable influence never cared and kept shooting and as a result BAN was there!', ''),
