(29140, ' This is a difficult situation, when these bandits come out to rob someone they have a huge advantage over their intended victims.\n\nI know many of my villagers that have been robbed on the way home at night on a dark country road some have been killed when the driver has tried to escape by speeding away, the robbers usually place large rocks in the road to halt the vehicle that they have targeted, then one or two approach the vehicle whilst the rest stay back and take aim with their AK 47''s.\n\nTo me it seems like  this is a no win situation if you are in the vehicle, even if your armed your like a sitting duck just waiting to be taken out.\n\nIn a situation like this my advice would be to surrender all valuables,I know the thread starter stated "if you are traveling alone" but imagine if you have family with you, even if you want to be a hero you must think of the women and children.\n\nThe only thing that might be of help in this situation is if your driving Abbas bhai''s Mercedes in which case you could turn around and drive off apart from that just comply with the criminals.\n\nThe hardest thing to hand over for me would be my pistol, especially if I was carrying a Glock :o\n\n\nMay Allah protect us from such highway robbers Aameen.', ''),
