(29293, ' AoA everybody\n\nmy advise to my brothers would be to:\n\n1. carry u''r CNIC everywhere u go\n2. carry u''r government issued service card (if any) everywhere u go\n3. carry u''r arms license everywhere u go (if u''r carrying any weapon)\n4. stay away from conceal carry style as it arises suspicion\n5. dont carry firearms during the imposition of 144.\n6. always give high priority to personal safety over style/manliness/macho-ness of carrying a live firearm.\n7. stay safe.\n\nRegards.', ''),
