(29425, ' [quote]Kaiser, That bird in the photo is not a saker, it''s a juvenile goshawk. How did it fly away? Was the cage left open?[/quote]\n\nThanks for giving me the real name of this falcon. Actually its sling broke & it flew away & I was taking shower at that time and there was nothing I could do. The very next day the chief hunting manager of Sheikh Zaid Bin Sultan Al-Nahyan was supposed to buy this bird from me but when I told him this bird was gone he was very upset because I sent a photo to Sheikh a few days before this event happened and Sheikh sent his manager by one of his private planes to Pakistan to bring this bird .. so he was really very much disappointed. When I asked him how much he would have paid me .. he told me he brought Rs 2,000,000/= (twenty lacs) .. this was 1987 and it was a big money at that time and this upsetted me a lot and I spent so many sleepless nights in regrets ... lol. I''ll try to find more photos of this bird and scan them and try to show them to you guys.', ''),
