(29446, ' InshAllah soon you guys will see some changes at PakGuns. Most notably new moderators, both I and FP are going to retire. With his new job FP won''t be able to give much time to PakGuns and this is incredibly busy work season for me. \n\nThe requirements are outlined below and I will be choosing two mods from our Senior members to replace us.  \n\n\n1). Only one Mod per city. i.e one from Karachi (must), one from Isb, Lahore or Peshawar.\n\n2). Prospective Mod should be a responsible individual and well liked by all PakGuns members.\n\n3). Must have the ability to be diplomatic, understanding and forgiving. \n\n4). Must be Completely and totally unbiased and neutral. \n\n5). Must be unconditionally loyal to PakGuns. \n\n6). Able to spend a few hours at PakGuns everyday.\n\n7). MUST HAVE THE ABILITY TO FOLLOW THE RULES SET FOR MODERATING THE FORUM.\n\n8). A sound knowledge of firearms is a plus although not an absolute requirement. \n\n\nPlease keep in mind that the persons I will ultimately choose will be because I think they will best fit the role for PakGuns not because I prefer them over other members.', ''),
