(29531, ' @all \n\nGuys i respect all your opinions, but i think you guys are missing the whole idea. At no point has abbas said FP or himself are being replaced as members or spearheds for this site. What he does suggest however is that he would require assistance of other senior members to help run the forum. Who would be their eyes and ears for the smooth sailing of Pakguns. \n\nI think it would rather very selfish of us to have both these key members comprise on their job to be on Pakguns as much as they used to be. The are professionals with commitments other than Pakguns, hence they need to prioritize their life and work . \n\nYour admiration for abbas and Fp are highly appreciated but do you think their decision to focus on other things in life would be a decision they would take lightly. I think not. We need to respect them and their choice and given them the confidence that with their guidance whom ever they decided to choose as moderation will do a good job. \n\nIMOH NOONE  is taking anybodies place, and i also think that it is not humanly possible for them to be here 24/7. This is our site and we need to share equal responsibility in maintaining the decorum of this site. \n\n@Abbas and FP.. Whom ever you decide to choose as a mod for this site has my full support. And i truly wish u the best in your work. Inshallah you will be able to take out time be with us on this forum. This is, was and will be your brainchild. \n\n\nRegards', ''),
