(30543, ' Salams all.\n\nIt is with great pleasure that I announce that PakGuns is now back online. A lot of stories will surely circulate as to what happened and I''m sure I will enjoy each and every version ;)\n\nA short and realistic explanation was that I was concerned about the legal status of PakGuns and I wanted to make sure we were on solid legal ground before we proceed further. Initially when I closed it I thought it would stay closed for good but with the dozens of emails that I continue to receive even today and the phone calls and the messages forced me to reverse my decision. PakGuns indeed has a special place in our hearts.\n\nA few minor changes will have to be made as per suggestion of our new lawyer. The first of which is that contact via PM''s and emails through the forum will be disabled, any and all and conversation will be done in the open forum. Nothing behind closed doors. The second change which I am considering implementing some time in the near future is the curtailing or completely disabling of the Marketplace section. InshAllah I will update as needed.\n\nWe will also have one or two new mods soon to help me manage PakGuns. I will InshAllah hand over most of daily forum running to them and move in the background and enjoy the forum just as any other member. \n\nI would like to thank each and every member personally from the bottom of my heart for their support. Almost all the emails that I received were extremely kind and each one had the tone of coming from a close friend. Again thank you very much and I''m sorry I could not reply all the mails.\n\nWelcome back !', ''),
