(30696, ' [quote=Irttyza]Im wondering if this would be classified as a double/twin O/U or SxS shotgun. :D[/quote]\n\n\nbrother it is classified as VIERLING (4 barrel combination shotgun). a combination shotgun can have multiple barrels of multiple calibers/gauges.\n\nexample:\n\n1. three shotgun barrels + one rifle barrel\n2. three rifle barrels + one 10/12/16/20 gauge barrel\n3. two rifle + two shotgun barrels\n4. any combination of 4 different/same type of gauges/cartridges u can think of.\n\na drilling is a combination shotgun that consists of three barrels in different/same calibers/gauge.', ''),
