(30905, ' Dear All PakGunners,  Congratulations to all on reopening of PakGuns .....I was very sad when i saw Abbas bhais post of closing it down.....I am very Happy that he choose not to.\n\n@Abbas Bhai ...... I was thinking of recommending  Starting of a Forum for Calculating the Cost of Running of the Website and Members can Donate according to their own wish...Plus you can also get some Advertising put on the website to Generate some revenue. But i would rather that we contribute on our own rather than have advertising. Also i would like to say that the Market Place Section should be retained as it gives New PakGunner Members like myself a good idea of the Prices of different Arms....Otherwise members can be hoodwinked into paying more without  having any idea of the prices of new or old weapons or otherwise cant compare, without any authentic reference prices available. But these are only my 2Cents. May Allah Bless You and Give you the Courage to Guide other Pakistani Youth  and Veterans on the Responsible use of Firearms. Ameen', ''),
