(30932, ' Whenever I''m away for a few days, there is always so much new to read. This time, it was interesting as well.\n\nI wish to write a short article on the events that took place after GLXSPK joined us with probably the largest or second largest gun collection among Pakguns'' members.  Since politics are not allowed as per rules, we''ll stick to being thankful that the forum is up & running again.\n\nI have always admired Abbas Sb''s vision, efforts & dedication towards this growing community of gun enthusiasts. To show my whatever little & symbolic support to him, I chose not to join the two forums that emerged as a reaction rather than inspiration to Pakguns policies & standards.\n\nInterestingly, I have never even met Abbas in person unlike most of our regular members.', ''),
