(381474, ' [QUOTE=selfdefence26;219986]Dear Brothers,\r\nI went last week to the Home Dept to make a computerized licence. I got there at about 10 am. You have to get a guest pass in order to enter Home Dept. Since the line was very long I got hold of a Police Constable and told him I want to enter. He refused first, but after some haggling allowed me to enter the building with a promise to give him some "Chai Pani" on my way back.\r\n\r\nOnce I entered, there was 3 or 4 other policeman near the entrance to the HOme Dept. They also asked me for a pass, but after talking with them, they also asked for Chai Pani. Promised them also for something on my way back.\r\n\r\nWent straight to the "Computerized Licences Dept". Quite straightforward from that moment on. First showed one guy copies of my original and photocopied Gas bill, PTCL bill and NTN Certificate. He looked at them (all in my own name) and told me to come along with him to the Section Officer Arms Mr.Peerbux for approval. He took me to his room which was filled with people. Anyways, managed to get approval within 10 mins and the SO signed on one of my docs for approval.\r\n\r\nAfter this, the person told me to go fill the Challan in National Bank Income tax branch which is close to HD. Got the form (photocopied from outside) and then attached my NIC copy and paid the Challan for Rs.4500/.\r\n\r\nAfter paying the challan then went again to HD and the person made me the Token (Just like nadra). After taking the TOKEN i went home because they was a lot of rush and I had to get to work soon.\r\n\r\nNext day I came to HD on Friday around 9.45 am. There was no one there except me. Took the photo and the other guy took out a printout of my details (just like passport printout) and then gave me a Verification form (Police) which is addressed to the SSP Verification branch/Special branch. This I asked is the Arambagh PS branch. Now the verification seems quite long. I hope to get some source to do the verification for me and will let u all know.\r\nAll in all a ONe day process if u have all yr docs.\r\nSD 26[/QUOTE]\r\n \r\nThank you brother for the information.', ''),
