(381466, ' [QUOTE=selfdefence26;219906]Hi Asif Brother,\nI have gone thru the process for The computerized licence. I have gone thru most of the procedure myself but I need help with the Police Verification. Can u help me?. Can u refer me to any dealer which can do the Police Verification for me?. I am willing to pay the dealer upto Rs.5K fr the genuine Police Verification Report. Or do u have any source or reference who can help me get the report within 12 days?. Thanks.\nSD 26[/QUOTE]\n \nFrom one of the guy in Arms section I asked complete package for Computerised License (C.L) and he asked around 15K (fee and verification included). There will be many in home deptt to help you, but it all depends on your personality (go in good executive dressing), where do you work, and negotiations skills.\nAnd forget about GENUINE VERIFICATION, because first of all the license is Computerised(so no chance of fraud), second you would be dealing directly with Home Deptt. personnel(so verification arranged by him would be Original).\nTo get help you can also visit dealers at Lucky Star or DAAD-Zamzama, they might help you!\n\n[B][U][COLOR=red]P.S.[/COLOR][/U][/B]\nPlease also mention detailed procedure you have so far gone through to Mr.Huzaifa including documents required and step by step procedure you followed etc.\nRegards', ''),
