(32531, ' @Moeen I also visited him two days ago and he had none. I even asked for the Ruger Mark III in particular and he told me they only imported 4 or 5 pieces about 8 months back and they were all pre booked.\n\nAnyway did an extensive range test of the Ruger today. What a pleasure to fire. I took 200 rounds today and even if I had taken 500 I''m sure I would have shot them all before coming home. \n\nThe pistol is "fantastically" accurate, my first shot was a bull at 15 M. I also fired about 50-60 rounds on the same chart at a high rate of fire the results are below. Target was at 15 M. \n\n[img]http://i262.photobucket.com/albums/ii99/AbbasMalik/Rugertarget.jpg[/img]\n\nZubair, MHMalik, HasanJamshed, SWaheed also had a go. They would be able to shed more light on it. \n\nAlso blew the crap outta all ''tooti''s'' at 15 M. If you can find this pistol, [b]Buy it[/b] right there and then.', ''),
