(32747, ' Dear Forum Members\nI am going to post some pictures of the stuff i always keep in my car.They always help me & make my life easier,when ever i got stucked in an emergency situation.Very simple tools & stuff yet very powerful.Remember Emergency can be happenned at any time,at any place and you never know when it can be happenned. \n[url=http://www.postimage.org/][img]http://img5.imageshack.us/img5/651/12311008.jpg[/img][/url]\nbangi cord,which is very useful,for holding things.12"long screw driver,can be used where small screwdrivers cant be reach.with a long handle less force is required.Saw blade can be used to cut hoze pipes,plastic pipes & rubber pipes.Plug pana for unscrewing powr plugs and it can also be used to unscrew tyre.Sand paper can be used in removing rust & dust from the parts of your car,its very useful to remove rust from the battery terminal.A piece of wire can be used to connect and establish a electric connection.if the parol & cng connection is disabled you can connect it directly with the coil by using these wires.Condoms,very useful for containning water,if you got stucked in an emergency situation,you dont have any container or pot you can store water in a condom. \n[url=http://www.postimage.org/][img]http://img13.imageshack.us/img13/8140/10973628.jpg[/img][/url]\nManual foot pump,its easily available from every hardware store,yet very useful item and it can give life to your flat tyre.You can also put air into the air bed,air pillow,air boat.i always keep it in my car.Small handy umbrella(in red color).Piece of rope,ropes,knives are always your best friend in an emergency situation.\n\n[url=http://www.postimage.org/][img]http://img6.imageshack.us/img6/748/21415955.jpg[/img][/url]\nJumer cables a very useful item to surivive in an emergency situation,whenever your car battery is dead you can re-activate it by using jumper cable connecting it to another car.jumper cables always help you, especially those people who travel to hill stations especially in winter i would like to suggest them always a set of jumper cables in theirs car.very cheap easily available from every hardware store average price is Rs.250 to 300\n\n\n[url=http://www.postimage.org/][img]http://img115.imageshack.us/img115/753/77444998.jpg[/img][/url]\nAnother very powerful tool for every car is a toe chain rope.its also very easily available from every good hardware store & some pathans hawkers are also selling it,you may find them on different chowks of rwp/isb city.avergae price is Rs.300 to 400.Toe chain rople can pull your car if its break down & like wise.\n[url=http://www.postimage.org/][img]http://img6.imageshack.us/img6/9382/32389346.jpg[/img][/url]\nwe must keep Torch in our car,many people keep them,in darkness light is your only survival.I myself like this head lamp,which gives me freedom to work freely with hands free under the bonut or under the car.7 led lights and light goes straight upto 15m.Very good headlamp.Easily available from a good general store.Price is also very nominal not more than Rs.150.These are 2 normal lighters,one with compass and it really works,compass reading is very accurate the other lighter is without compass but it works well.Remember when ever you got stucked in an emergency situation in winter or at night,Fire is your first survival.So using lighters you can start a fire.Some fire starters are also available for fire but still i could not get them in the local market (rwp/isb) maybe i will find it in peshawar.Firestarter is a magnesium rod which is striked by the knife or any metal and it produces sparks.So To start a fire you can use many options,like matches,water proof matches,lighters, & magnessium firestarters.I prefer lighters as they are easily available.\n[url=http://www.postimage.org/][img]http://img200.imageshack.us/img200/1496/49667150.jpg[/img][/url]\nwe must keep a knife in our car always,either its a big knife or a small pocket knife.i keep these knife always in my car.1st one is swiss army multi tool knife,the quality and finishing is amzing,very good tool.S&W pocket knife,i love it and i love the man who gifted it , i shall not mention his name but you all know him very well,his friendship is a treasure for me.2nd one is a normal paper cutter knife you may have seen it in every office,but its very useful tool and can do many jobs.3rd one is also a pocket knife and i really like it.Screw Driver set,must be in every car to fix any problem related to your car.I always keep it in my car.it has different styles of screw drivers +,-,tester etc etc.\n[url=http://www.postimage.org/][img]http://img200.imageshack.us/img200/9903/45485271.jpg[/img][/url]\nFolding showel,with saw,pick and showel,again i am very thankful to that friend who gifted it to me.Very useful item if your car got stucked in a sand or snow.it can done multiple jobs,very handy,and fits in just a 6" pouch.if you like car camping or hiking it can also help you.Survival hachete 3 in 1 a hammer,nail plier and small axe with rubberised grip and its so well balanced and very effective to cut small bunches.Easily available from any local hardware store.\n[url=http://www.postimage.org/][img]http://img188.imageshack.us/img188/3565/68281585.jpg[/img][/url]\nI always keep a jacket in my car,it can save you from cold if you got stucked in a hilly area.always keep it in your car.\n[url=http://www.postimage.org/][img]http://img238.imageshack.us/img238/1909/39426802.jpg[/img][/url]\nthis rain coat is very good gear to survive in a rainy situation.100% water prof with hud.\n[url=http://www.postimage.org/][img]http://img4.imageshack.us/img4/4985/17913618.jpg[/img][/url]\nwhenever u want to work on your car,wear gloves,they will save you from dust & oil and your hands shall remain neat and clean.in winter you can also wear them if you got stucked in a hilly area.\n\n[url=http://www.postimage.org/][img]http://img164.imageshack.us/img164/6052/14409346.jpg[/img][/url]\nAn air pillow,its very useful if u have to stay in out doors.very easily available.\n\n[url=http://www.postimage.org/][img]http://img14.imageshack.us/img14/3274/87462936.jpg[/img][/url]\nevery car must have a first aid kit, i got some ointment,different bandages,powder,tissues,safety pins,medical tape,saniplast,disprin tablets.atleast you can surive if you are got sick in outdoors.This medical kit is not 100% perfect but it may help you to give some treatment.\n\n[url=http://www.postimage.org/][img]http://img14.imageshack.us/img14/754/20260488.jpg[/img][/url]\nSleeping bag can be used as a blanket too.this is my very old sleeing bag which i bought in 1990,when i just passed my matriculation examination.Its not good for high altitude places but can work well in a normal temprature.Its local made got it from kabari bazar saddar,price i have forgotten,as its 19 years old.\nso this is my home made car+emergency survival kit.you can see that every item is very common but its performance is great especially in an emergency situation.You can find all these items in the local market very easily and at very nominal prices.The reason to start this thread is to make people life easier.I want all of you to plz be prepared to face any emergency situation.in normal life we dont care about these things and find them just a junk,but when we stuck in a bad situation then these  junky things get us life,comfort and ease.After collecting these gears now i am hopeful to face any emergency situation and these things work well,i have tested them.\n\nBe prepared!!!!!!!', ''),
