(32819, ' Salam Abbas bhai, not to insult the gun or you but.... WHAT ARE YOU ON ABOUT?????  Just 15 meters!!!!  Thats like stating proudly "my ferrari Enzo does 60mph!!!!"  I seriously think that you need to get out more with that pistol.  I shoot plates in isb gun club with speed and accuracy at distances so extreme most people think I am crazy until they see me shoot it.  Trust that pistol its meant for more than just 15m - try minimum 50m or more.  If you don''t believe me - then take a drive to ISB and meet me at the gun club, I WILL show you what that thing is capable of.  Ask Dr. Zakir, he has seen what this pistol can do.', ''),
(32820, ' .22 Long Rifle is known as the Assasins choice...  also like shown in the movie assassins with Sly, he is using the Ruger MKII Amphibious model by Gemtech.  Israeli Mossad personnel carry and train on Beretta Model 87s.  The IDF who guard the border walls also have on hand Ruger 10/22 rifles which they use to ruthlessly harm/maim individuals by shooting them in the knees or feet.  \nIn N. America its the main stay for teaching youngsters how to shoot.  Its a great practice round with cheap price and low recoil... plinker.    The average terminal range of .22 is over a mile.\nI love my .22s I have over ten... and am always out for more.  The last one I purchased is a serious contender/competitor of the ruger MKIII - I bought the Browning Buckmark Contour URX.  Check it out at Buksh Elahi, shoots as well as the Ruger... I was very very impressed.', ''),
(32821, ' [quote=Moeen]Salam Abbas bhai, not to insult the gun or you but.... WHAT ARE YOU ON ABOUT?????  Just 15 meters!!!!  Thats like stating proudly "my ferrari Enzo does 60mph!!!!"  I seriously think that you need to get out more with that pistol.  I shoot plates in isb gun club with speed and accuracy at distances so extreme most people think I am crazy until they see me shoot it.  Trust that pistol its meant for more than just 15m - try minimum 50m or more.  If you don''t believe me - then take a drive to ISB and meet me at the gun club, I WILL show you what that thing is capable of.  Ask Dr. Zakir, he has seen what this pistol can do.  [/quote]\n\nYou are right, the pistol is quite capable well beyond 15 M, perhaps you missed the part where I said I was [b]rapid[/b] firing and the first time  shooting this pistol. Anyway I would be more than happy to take a few shooting lessons from you and Dr. Zakir next time I''m in town as I truly have a great deal to learn. \n\nA little update about the assembly / dis assembly, it took about 5 minutes each way today now that I know exactly what to do. Still a bit annoying but a small price to pay for the peace of mind.', ''),
