(32823, ' @SanSyed, .17 is not a prohibited bore, actually i own .17 mach2 and .17HMR. These are on my NPB licences. .17 is the newest rimfire bore with some very interesting capabilities. Its very small 17 grain pallet has the muzzle velocity of more than 2200m/s, that is twice the speed of sound. Its tragectory is almost flat. More and more people are turning to this bore for varmint control(.17 mach2) and small game hunting(.17 HMR) because of their excellent accuracy and ballistics.', ''),
