(33852, ' A colleague of mine Mehroz Zafar wanted to hunt an Impala as well so we set out on a one day hunting mission \nWe left early on a Sunday\n[url=http://www.postimage.org/][img]http://img26.imageshack.us/img26/7259/44102129.jpg[/img][/url]\n\n[url=http://www.postimage.org/][img]http://www.postimage.org/gx1mzP29.jpg[/img][/url]\n\n[url=http://www.postimage.org/][img]http://www.postimage.org/gx1mA7_i.jpg[/img][/url]\n\nTarget practice session\n\n[url=http://www.postimage.org/][img]http://www.postimage.org/gx1mArXr.jpg[/img][/url]\n\nTarget looks like a tiny white spec at over 100 yrds\n[url=http://www.postimage.org/][img]http://img158.imageshack.us/img158/3770/45073727.jpg[/img][/url]\n\nTarget as seen through the bino\n[url=http://www.postimage.org/][img]http://www.postimage.org/gx1mAVT9.jpg[/img][/url]\n\n\n\nThe guide giving last instructions\n[url=http://www.postimage.org/][img]http://www.postimage.org/aVADNaA.jpg[/img][/url]\n\n[url=http://www.postimage.org/][img]http://img197.imageshack.us/img197/2118/49345867.jpg[/img][/url]\n\nAll set lock n load\n[url=http://www.postimage.org/][img]http://img4.imageshack.us/img4/1281/64339035.jpg[/img][/url]\n\nMaking it to the Impala in time to perform Zabiah\n[url=http://www.postimage.org/][img]http://img200.imageshack.us/img200/7320/74163562.jpg[/img][/url]\n\n[url=http://www.postimage.org/][img]http://img35.imageshack.us/img35/6842/45202734.jpg[/img][/url]\n\nStill breathing\n[url=http://www.postimage.org/][img]http://img269.imageshack.us/img269/5375/54865724.jpg[/img][/url]\n\nBetter than the last time\n[url=http://www.postimage.org/][img]http://img26.imageshack.us/img26/545/12120439.jpg[/img][/url]\n \naround 23" almost what I had in mind.\n[url=http://www.postimage.org/][img]http://img197.imageshack.us/img197/4229/17529189.jpg[/img][/url]\n\n[url=http://www.postimage.org/][img]http://img4.imageshack.us/img4/3897/37942313.jpg[/img][/url]\nShot it from around over a hundred yards with German mauser .243 with Bushnell scope\n\n[url=http://www.postimage.org/][img]http://img21.imageshack.us/img21/4229/61567388.jpg[/img][/url]\n\n[url=http://www.postimage.org/][img]http://www.postimage.org/aVAFks9.jpg[/img][/url]\n\n[url=http://www.postimage.org/][img]http://img200.imageshack.us/img200/3258/85283773.jpg[/img][/url]\n\nBack at the ranch house\n[url=http://www.postimage.org/][img]http://www.postimage.org/gx1mCbHJ.jpg[/img][/url]\n\n[url=http://www.postimage.org/][img]http://img21.imageshack.us/img21/2237/41561987.jpg[/img][/url]\n\n[url=http://www.postimage.org/][img]http://www.postimage.org/aVAWtv0.jpg[/img][/url]\n\n[url=http://www.postimage.org/][img]http://img33.imageshack.us/img33/6202/82984719.jpg[/img][/url]', ''),
