(33933, ' You are free to have your own opinion but I believe [b]I will not be firing a single shot when it is intended\n[/b] for a SD/HD purpose. And if God forbid I don''t get a chance for the second shot, then I''m sure even the\nfirst would have made no difference. Besides this I''m not sure about you guys, but I myself have never been\nin a SD/HD situation so far, but I''ve witnessed unintended discharges. Therefore, I feel more concerned about\nthose. This is my opinion and I think we are all free to have our own according to our thinking ;) \nAbout the cycling, if a blank doesn''t cycle properly, then I think I will abandon the idea.', ''),
(33934, ' Sir, how many murders are committed with licensed guns? Next to zero.\n\nI do not think licensed suppressors would be used for committing assassinations and what not..\n\n\nThe process of owning regularized and licensed firearms and accessories should be made simpler and not more cumbersome. In this country sadly it is easier to procure illegal full auto firearms than to own a legal licensed hunting rifle.\n\nTill this problem is not solved, lamentably, the crime rate cannot be controlled.', ''),
