(34165, ' [quote=PakistanGuides]Dear Friends\nI always respect everybody''s opinion but personally I think this so called entertainment in the form of arranged Dog filgts, Cock Fights or other animal fights is cruel, unethical and sadistic and casts bad psychological impact on humans by making them feel & behave like cold blooded humans which is not good for them & for the society. I would suggest pak guns not to encourage such threads since it derails our common interest for which we''ve got together on this forum ! ... by the way our "Off Topic Forum" has indefinite interesting topis that we can share without getting into controvercial topics.[/quote]\n\nAsalamalaykum,\n\nBrother I agree with everything you have said, but am wondering how you reconcile this with what you do,which is hunting live animals. We are only allowed to shoot animals in order for food.In your case you hunt for sport and some of the game you shoot and kill is haram to eat anyway.\n\n\nIt says in a hadeeth which was narrated from Ibn ‘Abbaas that the Messenger of Allaah (peace and blessings of Allaah be upon him) said: [b]“Do not use anything in which there is a soul as a target.” (Narrated by Muslim, 1957). \n[/b]\n\nI see from your picture that you have a full sunnah beard which tells me your a man who follows the quran and sunnah.\n\nSorry for this question my brother but I have been wondering about this for some time.\n\n\nI would appreciate your response', ''),
