(34428, ' [quote=PakistanGuides]Looks like I''m a "Black Crow" (FA Pass - BA Fail) among a flock of "White Pigeons" (So Many MBAs)\n\nBut I''m so lucky that Allah converted my hobby into my profession. I serve hunters, climbers & trekkers for just 3 months in a year & then I’m off for a long vacation of 9 months to eat, sleep & enjoy my life like a prince. \n\nMy mother used to say I’m a “3 Mahinay Ka Tajir & 9 Mahinay Ka Muhajir”. But if time is money in this busy world .. I’m the Bill Gates of Pakistan ![/quote]\n\nPG Brother don’t mind please, as u are a member of Pakguns that’s why I am giving you one suggestion. Its really really true that time is money no doubt about it. Failing in BA is not a big deal don’t worry about that just concentrate and appear again in the exams and work hard you will be Inshallah able to clear it. In my opinion a person should at least have masters degree.\n\nAnd as far as your nine months free time is concern bahee, it’s my brotherly advices please do utilize this time in any study or creative activities. \n\nPlease don’t mind as you are a member of Pakguns and all Pakguns members are like family and if my real brother is on your place I will definitely  advise him also. \n\nDo think about that \n\ncheers', ''),
