(34479, ' I bought this laser for Rs. 1500 and its working fine even after couple of hundred shots (not just few). Solid built, effective adjustments & value for money. I have other Chinese products in use as well without any issues. I suggest have your own opinion about something rather than asking those who just read reviews of the few unlucky ones abroad. This Chinese BAD BAD thing happened when Norinco handguns were introduced. After lots of unnecessary criticism trying & testing, now people swear by its quality & performance. \n\nOne more think I would like to add here before people jump into comparing apples with oranges, its a matter of choice & application. Some people buy things for their passion & not even application & some buy them for pure application and another group goes for both. Chinese products are cheaper and not the best quality in the world in terms of finish & features BUT its value for money & give as much results as any thing with same specs. Those who have used them will know it better.\n\nI hope it helps.\n[url=http://www.postimage.org/][img]http://img17.imageshack.us/img17/8159/31104903.jpg[/img][/url]', ''),
