(35397, ' [quote=Abbas]I generally just buy fabric/foam gun cases for all my shotguns/rifles. I like the fact that they are scratch proof, light weight, and provide a soft buffer in case of falls etc. \n\nHard cases do look better but are more expensive, less easily available, more difficult to transport and generally custom made for the weapon.   \n\nSoft cases are available from Rs. 600 (local) to Rs. 4000 (Uncle Mike etc).[/quote]\n\n\nI prefer a soft case over a hard one anyw day.. I can hug a shot gun to sleep with one of those', ''),
