(35453, ' [quote=Conceal Carry]I always carry whenever I am travelling with my family. \n\nI think I have good situational awareness. Late one night returing from a wedding when we reached near our home, I observed there was a taxi with 5 occupants parked just meters ahead of our main gate. Before I did anything my 5 year old daughter says, and believe me there is no exageration, "Dad there is that taxi parked in front of our home, take out your gun and go shoot them"[/quote]\n\n\nThats surely Cute! .........and Its good that kids these days are aware of the law and order situation in our country and know how to protect themselves and their families', ''),
