(35873, ' Though i am a gun enthusiast myself and do carry, but there are certain places I never carry, Office being one of them and for following reasons.\n1-Why?\n2-Why on person?\n3-Why let it be seen?\n\nI feel that this could very well be a threatening move / gesture by one person (office bully) to one or more other persons in the office, inspired by personal, official, religious or ethinic reasons. \n\n\nMy be the person who saw it, found out something fishy and he needed to be threatened discretely, and this weapon could be legal with liscence, permit and whatever it needs to be legal and legitimate. I am more concerned about the intentions of the move rather than the legality of the possession.\n\nIn many US states if your legal CC gun is printing (showing an outline underneath the clothing) and someone reports it to the police, the gun owner looses his liscence and CC permit because it is cnsidered a threat.\n\nCase still not decided. It''s very hard convincing the other two, my point if this person is let off, it would set a wrong  precedence and I my self wll start coming armed and carry the gun in my belt openly showing it to all, this part frightens the other two colleagues, I think I''ll prevail, InshAllah.', ''),
