(36181, ' [quote=Adeel Ahmad]\nI raised a concern that some young people might be getting involved in this forum and i never mentioned that any such thing is being shown here. I do not agree with you that a young enthusiast should be allowed here as if we were to give guns in hands of young people then there would not be age limit of 21.[/quote]\n\nAdeel bro, With due respect I have different opinion, we are not giving weapons in anyone''s hands here, just trying to develop a sensible gun culture & teaching gun ethics to one''s who already have guns in their hands, without age discrimination.\nI will be very comfortable with my sons reading & posting on this forum before they break in to my gun cabinet, at least they will have a comprehensive knowledge of gun safety and the responsibility when they have one in their hand. \nMy dear, the place we live in is full of guns, there are lot of people who easily can sell a gun to a minor but we donot have much sources available to teach the minors & adults aswell how to be responsible with a gun in hand.\nThat exactly to my opinion is the positive side of being on the forum like PG.', ''),
