(36341, ' [b]Not in comparison of bigger bores, but in itself[/b], .22 is a deadly & accurate caliber. Theory and anatomy apart, the biggest factor in BG situation is panic & its totally a different feeling than taking position, grip & breath control at 15 meter range. With extremely low recoil & flip, its dead accurate once pointed at something.\n\nSecondly, being a revolver will take care of any misfires without any FTF & FTE.\n\nWe are not comparing it with the bigger bores but even in itself its not a bad choice. It gives additional pleasure to shoot much more ammo and lot less noise.', ''),
