(36522, ' Adding an age limit to the forum will not be wise, in my humble opinion. You see, this forum exists as a powerful knowledge source for old and young gun enthusiasts alike. Today, in Pakistan, we talk about youth leadership, youth taking responsibility and the like. How are we supposed to do that if our elders do not trust us?\n\nBelieve me, Pakguns is probably the last place I can think of that can influence our youth in a bad way. In fact, it seeks to correct misguided souls which are either scared of guns or those who simply view them as tools for killing. \n\nAs for out of the way comments, I''m sure that our mods can take care of that. Responsibility should be shared by adults and youngsters alike.', ''),
