(36868, ' Mustanir, thanks for the welcome. \n\nAs a newcomer and guest in your house, I''m not familiar with how things are done here. Please excuse my ignorance. i have no intention of insulting anyone or jumping a queue.\ni8 am honored that so many members have welcomed me here.\n\nFinding this site has offered me an opportunity and a challenge to learn more about Pakistan and the firearms enthusiasts I had no idea existed.  \n\nMy very limited knowledge of Pakistan comes from early school years and more recently from the media, which is very often a poor source for accurate information.\n\nFinding this site has given me a huge personal project to explore Pakistan through the help and eyes of individuals who share my passions for hunting /firearms.\n\nI hope to be able to share some information about Canada from my experiences here, through the eyes of hunter/ firearms enthusiast.', ''),
