(36937, ' [quote=Bluff]@ 12guage.... consider the weight too... MP153 is app 1.3 KG heavier that Escot. :)\n\n@Turumti... bro try to find Escot.. super magnum ...... you ll find it better than escot \nthe difference is , the super magnum is 3.50" chambered  and escot imagnum s 3" Chambered.[/quote]\n\nbrother I''ve never noticed any significant weight difference in Hatsan Escort Trio and Baikal MP153. the difference that u quoted (app. 1.3KG) is too huge and utterly unthinkable.\n\nAllow me to write the actual difference in weight:\n\nBaikal MP153 outweighs the Hatsan Escort Trio by .3KG = 300grams = 0.66lb\nit doesnt seems like alot nor i''ve felt it to a degree that would make me re-think my preference for baikal MP153.\n\ndont take my word for it, here are the links:\n\n[url]http://www.baikalinc.ru/en/company/95.html[/url]\n[url]http://www.hatsan.com.tr/new_escort_trio.asp[/url]\n\njust remember to compare polymer with polymer and wood with wood.\n\n[b]one more thing: [/b]kindly post ur source (tel number of the dealer/name) for the 3.5inch super magnum, none of the dealers i know in ISB/RWP/PSH seem to know that a 3.5inch super magnum actually exists. even the website doesnt list any 3.5inch chambered Escort Super Magnum.\n\nRegards', ''),
