(37164, ' [quote]Good point and it make a lot of sense, but this would be seen by many as taking the long route, and in today''s society most people are  looking for the short cut. Its a case of I want it all and I want it now in this individualistic society that we find ourselves  living in.\n[/quote]\n\nspoken like a true genius brother\n\n[quote]Brother 12gauge what would be your ideal H/D shotgun from those models which are readily available in Pakistan?\n[/quote]\n\n\nhmmm... my ideal weapon for HD would be quiet honestly, in the order of preferance:\n\n1. Mossberg 590A1\n2. Mossberg 500\n3. Maverick 88\n4. DSA Security\n\nbut for all practical purposes, I would go for DSA Security as i''m a firm believer of Cost-Benefit Ratio and DSA comes on top if u consider the benefit that one can derive after factoring in the cost.\n\nRegards.\n\nP.S. had bought Mossberg 500, later sold mossberg 500, bought maverick 88, later sold maverick 88, bought one DSA (got another one as a gift), still retain two DSA. this should explain everything.', ''),
