(37481, ' [quote=CougarMan]how does the benelli handle local ammo?  there have been conflicting reports on its ability to manage with lower powered loads, what is your experience?[/quote]\n\nI have tried local #4 Shaheen with no problems.. Have hunted rabbits in Haripur with it.. Had no issues whatsoever..\n\nHowever out of about 30 #8 (the blue ones) I did have 2-3 FTEs.. But it did shoot.. it didnt cycle.. so it becomes a bolt action..\nIt wasnt designed for birdshot anyway..\n\nI am in love with its sound.. its an ARGO self cleaning dual gas piston system.. It cycles so fast people think its a full auto.. lol! But no shotgun has a sound like this one.. its just undescribeable.. not the BOOM.. the sound of the cycling and chambering.. Everyone who hears it just falls in love with this weapon.. (I know it sounds silly.. )', ''),
