(37488, ' [quote=Abu Al Hawl]guys when it comes to SD and FD, use best of the ammos, and trust me hydras will not let you down even if it will touch BGs'' finger. its a nuclear bomb for a human.[/quote]\n\nI''m sure my friend means that figuratively.. Now dont you all go and shoot the BG in the fingers with the hydra shocks.. :lol:\n\nAlways double tap.. ALWAYS try to hit the head, upper torso (what is known as a Centre of Mass)..\n\nFor practice, use silhouettes with human shapes rather than target types so you know better where you are hitting the person if need be.. and adjust accordingly.. Try to shoot so you can place 5 shots on target in at LEAST 10 seconds..', ''),
(37489, ' Everyone has personal habits, but it is not advised to mix ammo in same magazines.. \n\nIf you must, keep FMJs and JHPs in different magazines and ditto for all weapons\n\nIts a good habit I guess..\n\nFMJs perform much better when there are barriers such as heavy clothing, glass window etc if you have to engage target through such things.. JHPs lose energy rapidly when passing different mediums..\n\nIt depends on particular persons anticipated threat perception.. Do what is required and what you feel best suits you..', ''),
