(37776, ' I saw that you had linked one of my Youtube videos to the website, wanted to say, "hello," and you are welcome to the video.  \n\nETA:\n"Basic Principles of Proper Shooting" on this page: \n\n[url]http://www.pakguns.com/videos1.php[/url]\n\n\nA firearms instructor in the US state of Missouri uses the same video for his class there.\n\nI''ve posted several other videos, please visit, view, comment on, and rate them.\n\nSteven Cline\n:cool:', ''),
