(37788, ' Asalamalaykum brother Kaisar,\n\n\nBrother with all due respect I find it strange that you would object to the usage of the word Mosque even after I posted the articles that responded to the doubts raised.\n\nWhat you posted had already been responded to and refuted as being incorrect.If you had some new information to add to the discussion I would have been more than happy to reevaluate my position.\n\nPlease do not be offended by what I am saying, its just that it seems to me that you have ignored the refutation of the doubts and have continued to propagate that which has been answered in full.\n\n\nIf you take the time to read the articles I posted especially the second one,you will see that the doubts raised are not based on any facts rather they originate in a book titled [b]‘The Complete Idiot’s Guide to Understanding Islam’ [/b] which was written by a non Muslim who it seems was a complete idiot himself.\n\n\nKhair, anyway the title of the thread is back to what it was originally.Once again please don''t take offense I''m just trying to understand.\n\n\nWasalam', ''),
