(37804, ' [quote=Conceal Carry]If you are allowed to keep only one arm by a change in state laws, which of the following would be your choice and why?\n\nHandgun (any caliber Revolver or Pistol)\nRifle (any caliber Semi or bolt)\nShotgun (any guage Semi or Pump or single barrel or double barrel) \n\nPlease give your reasons.[/quote]\n\nRifle: I think an AR-10 might be a great all purpose end of the world scenario gun.  Hard hitting at many a distance, accurate enough for 300-500 yard shots.  Powerfull enough to take down most game animals and many prepators.  High capacity, a little heavy.  Would substitute a Springfield M1 without qualms.  Would accept an AK-47.\n\nHandgun: Glock 17, 22, or 21.  Simple platform, dependabilty, durable, resists elements well.\n\nShotgun: Mossberg pump in 12 guage.\n\nWould probably go with the shotgun for many of the same reasons as stated above.  Can shoot a variety of shells for a variety of purposes, bird, to deer with shot shell, slugs for nastier predators.', ''),
