(37806, ' [quote=StevenCline]I''ve been visiting the forums... many of the same threads could be right out of GlockTalk in the US.  Apparently gun-guys are gun-guys, no matter where they live.\n\nQuestion, if it can be asked, what is a prohibitted bore?[/quote]\nSteven:\nProhibited bores are calibers which fall under a prohibited category according to the firearm laws. These weapons can not be carried / licensed by  the public unless under special circumstances (security guards etc) when they are issued a prohibited bore license. and example is the ak.', ''),
