(38022, ' [quote=Silent killerr]which one is better between SPAS 12 and Benelli M3? comment with proper reasons[/quote]\n\n\ncant say about Benelli M3, it is pretty much a conventional semi auto (autoloader, recoil operated) outfitted with an option to manually cycle the loads (pump action) as well.\n\nMy uncle in village has a SPAS 12 and I''ve found the weapon to be just a beefed up conventional gas operated gun with a pump slide to manually cycle the load if the need arises. however, its heavy, its massive and too unwieldy to be practical. large, huge heatshield, large/huge forend and the internal action/system too complex.\n\n\nout of the two, SPAS looks mean (I think thats the only thing its worth for) whereas benelli M3 looks like a well design combat shotgun. sleak/slim/egronomic and well thought out design and carries a heavy punch. SPAS 12 i''m afraid, only looks mean.\n\nRegards', ''),
