(38181, ' [quote=Abu Hafs]What is a CNIC?\n\nIs it easier to make a provincial license? What about a home security license? \n\nThanks guys, and sorry for the dumb questions.[/quote]\nCNIC is Computerized National Identity Card not Citizen National Identity Card.\nIts only easier to get a Provincial License if you have direct relation with DCO otherwise the process is same. If you want Gaurds to use the weapon you can put his name on the Retainer Line.', ''),
