(38492, ' Ok guys i have been extremely lazy about posting the pictures and i do apologize for that. Here it goes people.\n\nNow by looking at the Water you cant see what is out there but actually there were two birds waiting to be shot :)\n[url=http://www.postimage.org/][img]http://img190.imageshack.us/img190/1232/96423330.jpg[/img][/url]\n\nNow here goes our first shooter with his Double Barrel for the kill\n[url=http://www.postimage.org/][img]http://img200.imageshack.us/img200/9996/26037728.jpg[/img][/url]\n\nNow comes the second shooter with his Desi Repeater. Its Desi so he is extremely Trigger Happy\n[url=http://www.postimage.org/][img]http://img12.imageshack.us/img12/2052/35827332.jpg[/img][/url]\n\nQuite a long walk for the Oldie Eehh\n[url=http://www.postimage.org/][img]http://img12.imageshack.us/img12/9057/33526844.jpg[/img][/url]\n\nTrigger Happy was just going on Adrenaline. Shoot, shoot and shoot\n[url=http://www.postimage.org/][img]http://img41.imageshack.us/img41/4627/46858454.jpg[/img][/url]\n\nDuring his huffing and puffing, Ahmad Bhai got it in the first shot :)\n[url=http://www.postimage.org/][img]http://img194.imageshack.us/img194/4602/82915418.jpg[/img][/url]\n\nFirst try for being happy on trigger\n[url=http://www.postimage.org/][img]http://img33.imageshack.us/img33/3863/69963504.jpg[/img][/url]\n\nHe was going for the third try but Ahmad Bhai got the second one as well :) Way to go you pro Shooter :)\n[url=http://www.postimage.org/][img]http://img16.imageshack.us/img16/3482/26031800.jpg[/img][/url]\n\nNow again you cant see anything but we fished out the first one and second one sunk in :(\n[url=http://www.postimage.org/][img]http://img41.imageshack.us/img41/5855/79068710.jpg[/img][/url]\n\nHere it is guys. Our hunt for that day :)\n[url=http://www.postimage.org/][img]http://img12.imageshack.us/img12/3830/27322750.jpg[/img][/url]\n\nMight not have been enough for all of us\n[url=http://www.postimage.org/][img]http://img31.imageshack.us/img31/8386/56695731.jpg[/img][/url]\n\nLets see, a Double Barrel belonging to Ahmad Bhai. Bird Killer :)\n[url=http://www.postimage.org/][img]http://img200.imageshack.us/img200/4489/15977986.jpg[/img][/url]\n\nNow you can understand why i call him Trigger Happy. He is ready to go one more time :)\n[url=http://www.postimage.org/][img]http://img43.imageshack.us/img43/4593/12660521.jpg[/img][/url]\n\nAhmad Bhai had some other plans. His .38 Revolver.\n[url=http://www.postimage.org/][img]http://img200.imageshack.us/img200/4153/42244033.jpg[/img][/url]\n\nBeauty isnt it\n[url=http://www.postimage.org/][img]http://www.postimage.org/aV1Sdvhi.jpg[/img][/url]\n\nAnd the Ammo for the mentioned .38\n[url=http://www.postimage.org/][img]http://img43.imageshack.us/img43/3056/34089323.jpg[/img][/url]\n\nJust take a look at the beast. Who needs Dirty Harry now baby :)\n[url=http://www.postimage.org/][img]http://www.postimage.org/gxb0tAJ.jpg[/img][/url]\n\nThe Revolver being handed to our Expert now. Lets see what he makes of it.\n[url=http://www.postimage.org/][img]http://img20.imageshack.us/img20/6703/31841279.jpg[/img][/url]\n\nAnd the Expert trying to look more Expert :)\n[url=http://www.postimage.org/][img]http://img33.imageshack.us/img33/8839/54131754.jpg[/img][/url]\n\nOh man, that smoke looks to be an Expert Creation :D\n[url=http://www.postimage.org/][img]http://img43.imageshack.us/img43/2383/84023080.jpg[/img][/url]\n\nOh God, not him again. People i was very scared taking his pictures.\n[url=http://www.postimage.org/][img]http://img188.imageshack.us/img188/8089/68759521.jpg[/img][/url]\n\nAnd during the whole escapade we again manged to kill something. A Scorpion.\n[url=http://www.postimage.org/image.php?v=PqyiqaA][img]http://img29.imageshack.us/img29/1640/36909266.th.jpg[/img][/url]\n\nOur most trusted and tried weapon. The .22 Rifle going at it again. Trigger Happy is just wishing he could squeeze the trigger :)\n[url=http://www.postimage.org/][img]http://img193.imageshack.us/img193/1503/27522122.jpg[/img][/url]\n\nNo Ahmad Bhai no, you are not a .22 person.\n[url=http://www.postimage.org/][img]http://img43.imageshack.us/img43/845/64331123.jpg[/img][/url]', ''),
