(38495, ' Another beauty owned by Ahmad Bhai\n[url=http://www.postimage.org/][img]http://img27.imageshack.us/img27/2306/85559051.jpg[/img][/url]\n\nNow my Glock 26 with Colt 1911\n[url=http://www.postimage.org/][img]http://img22.imageshack.us/img22/1638/97614986.jpg[/img][/url]\n\nColt 1911 and its Ammo\n[url=http://www.postimage.org/][img]http://www.postimage.org/aV1ShgeS.jpg[/img][/url]\n\nSome of the weapons we were carrying. War man War.\n[url=http://www.postimage.org/][img]http://img22.imageshack.us/img22/9530/58573247.jpg[/img][/url]\n[url=http://www.postimage.org/][img]http://img194.imageshack.us/img194/7084/54017191.jpg[/img][/url]\n\nJust look at the pretty pretty Ammo\n[url=http://www.postimage.org/][img]http://img188.imageshack.us/img188/8615/20919225.jpg[/img][/url]\n\nFinally Tareen Bhai got bored and started digging stuff from ground.\n[url=http://www.postimage.org/][img]http://img22.imageshack.us/img22/671/67798913.jpg[/img][/url]\n\nOh my bad, never knew he could also do that. I think that this says it all about the class of Tareen Bhai.\nNow people do look closely as it also shows my prowess as a Photgrapher. You can see the Shell coming out while the Rock is in air and also the slugs traveling towards it. :cool: After all it was taken from my N96. You can just imagine the results if i had my SLR on me.\n[url=http://www.postimage.org/][img]http://img190.imageshack.us/img190/1543/96089055.jpg[/img][/url]\n\nNow following pictures are something which i was told not to post but i am posting anyway. You can think of a caption yourself. Cheers :)\n[url=http://www.postimage.org/][img]http://img43.imageshack.us/img43/694/47872236.jpg[/img][/url]\n\nCant help myself by being amused while looking at following migration :)\n[url=http://www.postimage.org/][img]http://img31.imageshack.us/img31/7553/37306520.jpg[/img][/url]', ''),
