(38626, ' This happens few months before when me and my wife and two kids were coming back from a friend’s sister wedding. It was around 2:30 am and both of my kids went to sleep in a car’s back seat when we left for home. As I am living with my parents but in a separate portion which is at the backside of the house. \n\nAs soon as I reach in my street I noticed that two persons with a motorbike were standing in front of a house, which was 4 houses away from my home. I stop the car in front of my home and my wife got out opens the door and I rushed the car into the porch. While my wife was opening the door I was noticing the two guys standing 4 houses after my home. \n\nAfter going in and locking the doors I got on the roof and start watching both of then as my sixth sense was telling me that there is something going wrong as the occupants of that house were a man and his wife with one son and a mother and a father.\n\nI was standing on the roof and after 10 mints both the boys start pushing their bike and after obtaining some distance they start the motorcycle and went away. I waited for almost next 15 mints and then I came down and change my cloths and was preparing to going to bed. \n\nI have routine that before going to sleep I check all the doors and windows of the house and lock the main gate my self. So I did the same and after that I went up on the roof and saw that a car was standing in front of that house and a boy who was previously on the motorbike was standing next to the car. \n\nAs I was noticing all that I saw that one BG came out of the car and jumped into that house. After seeing this I just rushed down to call the police as my cell was not with me and picked up my 12 gauge shotgun and start running on the roof and after coming on the roof I simply fire 3 shots one after another in air and forth one on the car and moved back. \n\nAs soon as I fired the 4 shots, (the bang was so powerful at 3:00 or 3:15 am) that BG comes out of that house from the main gate and just rushed out in hurry and then I came to know that they were not two they were actually 5. \n\nOne was sitting in the car, one was standing outside the car and one was standing inside the house right in front of the main gate and other two were I think was busy to get them inside the house', ''),
