(39095, ' Its all abut the company rules and the nature of company, Now adays mostly every company have security system and security gaurds, They don''t allow any person or employe to carry an arm in the company permises,Before entering the company or in private business centres and plaza they have rule to deposit our weapon at entrance to the security gaurd. Must culture If his living style demands that he carry a gun, he should be follow the rules of companay or organisation during work.\nIn mostly government semi government and also private offices private buildings plazas shopping centers have our own security guards and system, sometimes due to misunderstanding,enemy or by personal matters they lodge a FIR as docaity robbery or harrasment against arm holder, Must be careful about everything to carry a weapon to any office,anybody home or at any sesitive place', ''),
