(39825, ' [url]http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=15qsJgnm0sw[/url]\n\nNomi, The above video will give u an idea about CF-98, how it feels in the hand and about its recoil. Its a good weapon, not very heavy, just like the latest western guns of about .0750 gram weight empty, the dis-assembly & assembly is easy, can be used rough and tough, can fire any kind of round, russian, chinese, POF, western. The firing mechanism is just like the Stoegar 8000 model. This weapon has been adopted by the Bangladesh Army, Chinese Army in the 5.8mm version, Hong Kong Police, Chinese Police and their counter terrorism units. \nI do hope this weapon would just perform like the Chinese TT did for so many decades.\nPrice is also very good these days, has come down to 30K here, peshawar i mean, dont know about the other cities. \nIf u wana go for chinese, then this is the best one.', ''),
